=========================================
C++ INTERVIEW ROADMAP (10+ YEARS EXP)
Most Important → Least Important
(C++11 Topics Removed)
=========================================

1. OOPS ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
-----------------------------------------
Topics:
- Class vs Object
- Encapsulation
- Abstraction
- Inheritance
- Polymorphism
- Virtual Functions
- Pure Virtual Functions
- Abstract Classes
- Runtime Polymorphism
- Compile-Time Polymorphism
- Function Overloading
- Operator Overloading
- Virtual Destructor
- Object Slicing
- VTable / VPTR

Must Know Questions:
- Why destructor should be virtual?
- What is object slicing?
- How does virtual function work internally?
- Difference between overloading and overriding?
- Can constructor be virtual?

=========================================

2. Memory Management ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
-----------------------------------------
Topics:
- Stack vs Heap
- new/delete
- new[]/delete[]
- Memory Leaks
- Dangling Pointer
- Wild Pointer
- Double Delete
- RAII
- Placement New

Must Know Questions:
- Difference between stack and heap?
- What causes memory leak?
- What is RAII?
- What is placement new?

=========================================

