TOP 10 HIGHEST ROI TOPICS
-----------------------------------------
1. OOPS
2. Memory Management
3. Smart Pointers
4. Copy Control (Rule of 3/5/0)
5. Move Semantics
6. STL Containers
7. STL Algorithms
8. Multithreading
9. Templates
